TRIP TO KASHMIR
(10pax= 8000/= ) (6 pax = 8250/=) ( 4pax = 9250/=) (2 pax = 13500/=)

5 NIGHTS & 6 DAYS With ( Breakfast & Dinner)
2 Nights Stay In Hotel Naqash Residency/ Similar Srinagar
1 Night Stay In Hotel Apple Tree/ Similar Gulmarg
1 Night Stay Hotel lidder View/ Similar Pahalgam
1 Night Stay In Houseboat
All transfers and sightseeing by Itios/ Tavera/ Tata Winger 
Day 1: Arrival at Srinagar and city tour- On arrival at srinagar, you will meet our representative andÃ‚ proceed for Mughal Gardens visiting Nishat Bagh and Shalimar Bagh. All the gardens are situated on the bank of Dal Lake with the Zabarwan Mountains in the background. The distance from Srinagar to the said gardens is about 12 and 15 kms respectively. Enroute visit carpet-weaving factory and old Srinagar city. Overnight stay at hotel/ houseboat.

Day 2: Sonmarg day trip- After breakfast, drive to Sonmarg. Full day excursion to Sonmarg. Sonmarg is known as "Gateway of Ladakh". In the evening return to Srinagar for overnight stay at hotel/ Houseboat.

Day 3: Srinagar to Gulmarg (56 kilometers / 2-3 hrs drive)- After breakfast, check out from the hotel and proceed towards Gulmarg. Enroute you get to see the beautiful Tangmarg town and drive ahead on a scenic drive of 14 kilometers to Gulmarg. Arrive in Gulmarg early in the afternoon and check in at the hotel. Later, begin a short tour, boarding the Gondola cable car system (the 08 minutes ropeway, at your own cost). Descend back to Gulmarg after an hour and later indulge in some horse-riding. Stay overnight at the hotel.

Day 4: Gulmarg to Pahalgam (152 kilometers / 4-5 hrs drive)- After breakfast, check out from the hotel and we drive to Pahalgam via Pampore, Avantipura and the village of Bijbehara which remains famous as the bread basket of Kashmir. We switch from the national highway 1A at Khanabal and drive through the second largest city of Anantnag. From here the road turns scenic as we drive parallel on the Lidder river flowing from the opposite direction. In Pahalgam, check-in at the hotel and spend the rest of the day at leisure. Overnight stay at the hotel.

Day 5: Pahalgam to Srinagar- After breakfast, check out from Pahalgam and drive to Srinagar. Overnight stay at Hotel/ houseboat.

Day 6: Drop at Srinagar Airport- After breakfast, check out from the hotel and drive to Srinagar Airport for your onward journey with memories of Heaven Trips.

1 Night Stay In Hotel Apple Tree/ Similar Gulmarg

Day 1: Arrival at Srinagar and city tour- On arrival at srinagar, you will meet our representative andÃ‚ proceed for Mughal Gardens visiting Nishat Bagh and Shalimar Bagh. All the gardens are situated on the bank of Dal Lake with the Zabarwan Mountains in the background. The distance from Srinagar to the said gardens is about 12 and 15 kms respectively. Enroute visit carpet-weaving factory and old Srinagar city. Overnight stay at hotel/ houseboat.

Day 2: Sonmarg day trip- After breakfast, drive to Sonmarg. Full day excursion to Sonmarg. Sonmarg is known as "Gateway of Ladakh". In the evening return to Srinagar for overnight stay at hotel/ Houseboat.

Day 3: Srinagar to Gulmarg (56 kilometers / 2-3 hrs drive)- After breakfast, check out from the hotel and proceed towards Gulmarg. Enroute you get to see the beautiful Tangmarg town and drive ahead on a scenic drive of 14 kilometers to Gulmarg. Arrive in Gulmarg early in the afternoon and check in at the hotel. Later, begin a short tour, boarding the Gondola cable car system (the 08 minutes ropeway, at your own cost). Descend back to Gulmarg after an hour and later indulge in some horse-riding. Stay overnight at the hotel.

Day 4: Gulmarg to Pahalgam (152 kilometers / 4-5 hrs drive)- After breakfast, check out from the hotel and we drive to Pahalgam via Pampore, Avantipura and the village of Bijbehara which remains famous as the bread basket of Kashmir. We switch from the national highway 1A at Khanabal and drive through the second largest city of Anantnag. From here the road turns scenic as we drive parallel on the Lidder river flowing from the opposite direction. In Pahalgam, check-in at the hotel and spend the rest of the day at leisure. Overnight stay at the hotel.

Day 5: Pahalgam to Srinagar- After breakfast, check out from Pahalgam and drive to Srinagar. Overnight stay at Hotel/ houseboat.

Day 6: Drop at Srinagar Airport- After breakfast, check out from the hotel and drive to Srinagar Airport for your onward journey with memories of Heaven Trips.

TRIP TO KASHMIR
(10pax= 8000/= ) (6 pax = 8250/=) ( 4pax = 9250/=) (2 pax = 13500/=)
DIAL:- +91-9086222333, +91-7006907797 ,
5 NIGHTS & 6 DAYS With ( Breakfast & Dinner)
3 Nights Stay In Hotel Royal Batoo/ Similar 
1 Night Stay Hotel Lidder Resorts / Similar Pahalgam
1 Night Stay In Houseboat
All transfers and sightseeing by Itios/ Tavera/ Tata Winger 

Day 1: Arrival at Srinagar and city tour- 
On arrival at Srinagar, you will meet our representative and  proceed for Mughal Gardens visiting Nishat Bagh and Shalimar Bagh. All the gardens are situated on the bank of Dal Lake with the Zabarwan Mountains in the background. The distance from Srinagar to the said gardens is about 12 and 15 kms respectively. Enroute visit carpet-weaving factory and old Srinagar city. Overnight stay at hotel/ houseboat.

Day 2: Sonmarg day trip- 
After breakfast, drive to Sonmarg. Full day excursion to Sonmarg. Sonmarg is known as "Gateway of Ladakh". In the evening return to Srinagar for overnight stay at hotel/ Houseboat.

Day 3: Gulmarg Day Trip
After breakfast, check out from the hotel and proceed towards Gulmarg. Enroute you get to see the beautiful Tangmarg town and drive ahead on a scenic drive of 14 kilometers to Gulmarg. Arrive in Gulmarg early in the afternoon and check in at the hotel. Later, begin a short tour, boarding the Gondola cable car system (the 08 minutes ropeway, at your own cost). Descend back to Srinagar after an hour . Stay overnight at the Srinagar hotel.

Day 4: Srinagar to Pahalgam 
After breakfast, check out from the hotel and we drive to Pahalgam via Pampore, Avantipura and the village of Bijbehara which remains famous as the bread basket of Kashmir. We switch from the national highway 1A at Khanabal and drive through the second largest city of Anantnag. From here the road turns scenic as we drive parallel on the Lidder river flowing from the opposite direction. In Pahalgam, check-in at the hotel and spend the rest of the day at leisure. Overnight stay at the hotel.

Day 5: Pahalgam to Srinagar- 
After breakfast, check out from Pahalgam and drive to Srinagar. Overnight stay at Hotel/ houseboat.

Day 6: Drop at Srinagar Airport 
After breakfast, check out from the hotel and drive to Srinagar Airport for your onward journey with memories of  Heaven Trips.

2 Nights Stay in Hotel Lalit The Grand Palace ( Breakfast )

1 Night Stay in Hotel The Khyber Himalayan Resort ( Breakfast )

1 Night Stay in Hotel Pine N Peak Pahalgam ( Breakfast )

1 Night Stay In Houseboat
All transfers and sightseeing by Itios/ Innova

Day 1: Arrival at Srinagar and city tour- 
On arrival at Srinagar, you will meet our representative and  proceed for Mughal Gardens visiting Nishat Bagh and Shalimar Bagh. All the gardens are situated on the bank of Dal Lake with the Zabarwan Mountains in the background. The distance from Srinagar to the said gardens is about 12 and 15 kms respectively. Enroute visit carpet-weaving factory and old Srinagar city. Overnight stay at hotel/ houseboat.

Day 2: Sonmarg day trip- 
After breakfast, drive to Sonmarg. Full day excursion to Sonmarg. Sonmarg is known as "Gateway of Ladakh". In the evening return to Srinagar for overnight stay at hotel/ Houseboat.

Day 3: Srunagar to Gulmarg
After breakfast, check out from the hotel and proceed towards Gulmarg. Enroute you get to see the beautiful Tangmarg town and drive ahead on a scenic drive of 14 kilometers to Gulmarg. Arrive in Gulmarg early in the afternoon and check in at the hotel. Later, begin a short tour, boarding the Gondola cable car system (the 08 minutes ropeway, at your own cost).  Stay overnight at hotel in Gulmarg.

Day 4: Gulmarg  to Pahalgam 
After breakfast, check out from the hotel and we drive to Pahalgam via Pampore, Avantipura and the village of Bijbehara which remains famous as the bread basket of Kashmir. We switch from the national highway 1A at Khanabal and drive through the second largest city of Anantnag. From here the road turns scenic as we drive parallel on the Lidder river flowing from the opposite direction. In Pahalgam, check-in at the hotel and spend the rest of the day at leisure. Overnight stay at the hotel.

Day 5: Pahalgam to Srinagar- 
After breakfast, check out from Pahalgam and drive to Srinagar. Overnight stay at Hotel/ houseboat.

Day 6: Drop at Srinagar Airport 
After breakfast, check out from the hotel and drive to Srinagar Airport for your onward journey with memories of  Heaven Trips.
